questions.scenario:
You are debugging a production issue where a Spring Boot microservice experiences a heap-based `OutOfMemoryError` during a nightly batch processing run. The following service class processes updates for thousands of records:

java
@Service
public class AccountService {
    @PersistenceContext
    private EntityManager em;

    @Transactional
    public void updateAccounts(List<Long> accountIds) {
        for (Long id : accountIds) {
            Account acc = em.find(Account.class, id);
            acc.setStatus("ACTIVE");
            // business logic
        }
    }
}
